{"tid":2095961,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[財經台故] 因為股票tips 同人發生左關係","createTime":"2020-07-06T00:31:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T06:12:16.000Z","uid":158008,"like":3,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9866fb4aaadb29efa57e22808f65a430aeb88c32","tid":2095961,"uid":158008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T00:31:15.000Z","msg":"我喺新界區一座舊工廠大廈做嘢，因成日有紙皮同廢鐵唔要，所以就同一個清潔阿姊熟起來。阿姊叫萍姊，佢身裁一D都唔平<br />\n<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/smile_47.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_47.gif&h=60d2baf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n，佢大約40尾，個樣其實好普通，黑黑實實，不過佢有時烏地身時，見到佢對奶巧很大同好濕（汗）  每次當有大量紙皮時（拆貨後）我都叫佢食飯時來收（因佢可以自己賣），有時佢會帶埋飯盒來一齊食。公司成日得我一個人，又有電視同冷氣，所以佢都經常上來食飯同蛇王。 萍姊成日問我成日食自己（指食飯） ，唔悶咩，我話無計啦，你泥多D囉。（見佢陰陰笑） 有次食飯睇電視報財經，佢問我有無買股票，我話有，佢話想買，但唔知買乜，跟住我推介左隻（其實睇報紙）。點知HiHi隻股票幾日內3嗰幾升到5蚊，佢更係開心啦（我無買扮買左）贏左幾仟蚊。遲幾日佢買佢飯盒同啤酒來，話就話多謝我，其實想攞貼士"},{"pid":"c8cc15669c64ecbbd4838a6a83b62e4e2d9297f0","tid":2095961,"uid":210463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T00:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fce5e09e5808462bb4bb6584fe4eda679af4a41","tid":2095961,"uid":34641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T00:34:03.000Z","msg":"恐山安娜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"620d0e561cc32ec07d4f89aed106aa93153720e1","tid":2095961,"uid":158008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fce5e09e5808462bb4bb6584fe4eda679af4a41","tid":2095961,"uid":34641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T00:34:03.000Z","msg":"恐山安娜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T00:34:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d9119a3e3846ddb9c7fd82cb598d61d612ada8","tid":2095961,"uid":158008,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T00:35:35.000Z","msg":"好，繼續。首先交待上回情節，當我一洩如注腳軟軟後，並?有出現電影股劇情；如什麼&ldquo;你好勁，悔開二度，用個囗?干?我細佬?情節。萍姐只係速速?番佢條阿婆底同肉色簿洛，就低頭想離開之際，我手拉?萍姊隻手，當然唔係比肉金或吊多鑊啦，而係比左張寫住&ldquo;8xxx,少注&rdquo;股票no.?紙比佢。隻股票名我聽都未聽過，係?隔離版青蛙兄吹過?一個no.跟住往後二日，隻股又無乜升又無乜跌，萍姐又無蒲頭同上來食飯盒，直至第三日午飯二，三點後，我睇財經電腦報價，比萍姐隻股票突然有異動（自己都買少少），哽係升動啦，都升巧多架，夠我食幾日KFC。咁我就渣渣淋用電腦放左隻股，就落停車埸?阿萍姊話比佢聽。"},{"pid":"f01dd51dcde7e99c615356a884d583e3dee8cc07","tid":2095961,"uid":47658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T00:42:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200fbdb1396044202f1c25d29d3c752830116814","tid":2095961,"uid":56550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T00:50:01.000Z","msg":"屌你地班耆齡王user<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56db58ae5d878d567edceca202071732b332f2f","tid":2095961,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T01:04:46.000Z","msg":"條友反而冇係呢個po貼圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n合晒合尺喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e121c8f543a1a22bacc799a96cf8eb29879c106","tid":2095961,"uid":308853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T02:10:18.000Z","msg":"冇咗重要嘅情節呀，仆街"},{"pid":"c89b95b89ec44d44032748e0246eebab54c95401","tid":2095961,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T02:24:45.000Z","msg":"ＰＵＳＨ"},{"pid":"a8ffb113466f27a64f5c772c3ce024e22d36d91d","tid":2095961,"uid":158008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e121c8f543a1a22bacc799a96cf8eb29879c106","tid":2095961,"uid":308853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T02:10:18.000Z","msg":"冇咗重要嘅情節呀，仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T02:32:18.000Z","msg":"我寫得唔好 講返多少少:<br />\n<br />\n食飯時，佢又問我no.，我話我D係內幕貼士，唔會亂甘比人（作的），跟住佢話會對我好D,<br />\n我更係食住上問佢點好D,點知佢話買埋生果比你（心想係咪你對木瓜）。<br />\n&ldquo;好啊，諗諗先&rdquo;，佢見我冷漠回應，加2錢肉緊話，你成日搬野，等我幫你按下骨啦，我即時色心頓起，冷漠回應；<br />\n又好。立即用張被放落地下，訓直地下睇佢點按。<br />\n仆街點知惡夢開始，佢當我係廢鐵同爛銅，見世色不妙，立即叫停。佢見唔對路，問我係咪唔舒服，<br />\n我話梗係啦，咁撚大力，按撚死我咩。<br />\n我見佢話唔好意思，我食住上話，我成日比人按知點按，我幫你按先，<br />\n你記住啦（扮專家同抽佢水）。<br />\n跟手叫佢訓直，按二按同佢講，你件衫好濕（汗），點按？叫佢除左件衫按啦。佢諗左諗，我話按摩係甘，同埋無人睇到，佢就除左件污穢衫，除剩個肉色barbar."},{"pid":"8cfa7f2cca0b8f61453257f8c7e9ff173dc276be","tid":2095961,"uid":65457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T04:02:28.000Z","msg":"幾多年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a8bec01071eea18ae5fe3647a5fe9c5930fd0ed","tid":2095961,"uid":180251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T04:04:51.000Z","msg":"40尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60d16c6c70a8ffb6296f6e087f65d358cc79490","tid":2095961,"uid":71632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T04:06:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/smile_47.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_47.gif&h=60d2baf3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/smile_47.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_47.gif&h=60d2baf3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/smile_47.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmili